    <p>{`This functionality allows either a `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "https://www.notion.so/Registration-Agent-7fe5e31c8fae4d3981e0d4f69576c084"
      }}><strong parentName="a">{`Registration Agent`}</strong></a>{` or `}<a parentName="p" {...{
