      }}><strong parentName="a">{`Registrar`}</strong></a>{` to print a certificate, either with or without digital certificates.`}</p>
    <Video url="https://www.loom.com/embed/f04130bd98364626aee0c51bf127d5e7" mdxType="Video"></Video>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "configuration"
    }}>{`Configuration`}</h2>
    <p>{`The certificate can be formatted as per a country's requirements. OpenCRVS also has a `}<em parentName="p">{`recommended`}</em>{` certificate based on global best practice.`}</p>
    <p>{`The ability to use digital signatures on certificates, print the certificate in advance for handwritten signatures or print on collection.`}</p>
